A video of the former Nigeria President, Chief Olusegun Aremu Obasanjo dancing with the master of ceremony at an event, Doyin Kukoyi has surfaced online. In the video, Obasanjo’s strength while dancing with the lady has attracted reaction from many people that saw it.
A Nigerian TV host, Doyin Kukoyi recently shared a video of herself dancing with the former Nigeria President, Olusegun Obasanjo in an event through her Instagram page. Many people were surprised at his vigour while dancing with this lady.
Doyin Kukoyi wrote on her verified Instagram page, “I requested for a dance and without hesitation, he granted me. Ladies and gentlemen, my dance with the former Nigeria President, Chief Olusegun Okikiola Aremu Obasanjo”.
What people observed in this video was the strength of the man while digging to the tune of the music being played for them to dance to. Some commend Chief Olusegun Aremu Obasanjo for his dancing steps. 
Watch the video HERE
A follower of the TV host wrote, “Baba was a good dancer”. Another one also wrote, “Nice one, grandpa never forget how to dance”. However, a follower wrote, “He’s so energetic and still very active”. Check some of the comments made on the video below



